item.description: Khalil Mack The Super Bowl has just occurred. One team is elated, one feels defeated, 30 are somewhere on a spectrum of “come on boys; next year is our year, for sure”, and “hey, we had no hope this year but at least we get great picks at the draft!” While the season is still on everyone’s minds, the League gives its players a questionnaire with a simple question: name the top 100 players in the league this season!
